                    <span>This book covers an amazing amount of material with a fun, down-to-earth writing style.<P>I mostly referenced this book for specific effects as I needed them, each chapter is kind of like a stand alone tutorial, very easy to follow and actually implement in your own code.<P>You can make a 3d game with this, I did.</span>
                  
